Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more month until the performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Time sure flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand at all, Kagura Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}do{\i0} understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you pluck a large star, you will obtain a great wealth."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Her noble spirit, refusing to relent and facing the tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,even after losing her memories and being cast into darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That strength of Claire's is what mesmerizes the audience and spurs them to face life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the very {\i1}soul{\i0} of the tale that is Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,During the 99th Seisho Festival last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept the glimmer of her soul at the forefront of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In acting, singing, and dancing—at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Kagura Hikari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel none of that from {\i1}your{\i0} Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't see the Starlight we put on back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true: both the script and direction are different from last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's go, to pluck that star together!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you pluck a small star,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you will gain a small amount of happiness."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even having lost her memories, she still remembered the promise she made with her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} is Claire's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However, even in the darkness when I had lost everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,she never abandoned me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She led me by my empty hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She waited for me and accepted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tendo-san? Kagura-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so obvious that it didn't occur to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can accept your way of constructing the character.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, both of you, calm—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It pains me to admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was more emotionally invested in Claire than I had thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the lead role?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be my first time seeing you in something other than a lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that might be why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been plays where I couldn't get a lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd taken that frustration to heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to sing and dance the boldest, so as to not lose to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,be frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At not getting a lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten the very thing I was trying not to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were we taking these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The prep room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm frustrated!{that was... awkward...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting tacks in your shoes, hiding your costumes, ignoring you on purpose...{I love the VA's performance here}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...is what I feel like doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagura Hikari-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, both you, right now—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've had it done to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You have?!{lmao at junna's confusion in this scene}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I do understand that feeling.{the past tense is tripping me up. when exactly did she come to understand that feeling?}{when the scrub girls she beat started bullying her, I assume. but I don't think there's anything lost in using a more straightforward present tense line}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Kagura Hikari-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been egotistical, forcing my feelings on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems I care more deeply than I'd realized
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for Claire and for Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I love them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen Tendo-san so frustrated before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or seen Kagura-san talk about herself so much, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous of you both, getting to play a lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not begrudging you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm not a lead character,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing that exceeds the joy of being on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"We may not have the same amount of time on stage, but we have the same glimmer."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a great saying, Hoshimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say my...{is this right? has hikari really never spoken her name before?}{no idea}{pretty sure it is; she basically just says Karen/Bakkaren and that's it}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm most grateful, Kagura Hikari-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for stealing the lead role from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If your acting is not up to par, I will steal my Claire back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tendo Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on.{dooon to koi desu! *slaps chest*}{don't koi}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bring it on", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The strong Claire...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the thankful Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
